author: jfernan2
body:
The unpacker itself lives in directory EventFilter/DTuROSRawToDIgi. 
This contains the packer and the unpacker for the complete CMS (as it will be after installation). Also an unpacker version for the uROS slice test is included (DTuROSRawToDigi2.h and .cc).

Also there is a directory called DataFormats/DTDigi that contains a new class to store the uROS control data and errors, to be used in the DQM.
title: DTuROS unpacker version
